# Create Dummies or One Hot Encoding for Categorical Attributes
hr_data_aft_ohe = hr_data

for var in cat_cols:
    cat_list ='var'+'_'+var
    cat_list = pd.get_dummies(hr_data[var],prefix=var)
    hr_data_aft_ohe=hr_data_aft_ohe.join(cat_list)
